        <mxCell id="LZzTBMvUempXx9omUjw9-10" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;The 100-point Matching Engine computes a compatibility score between each pair of profiles:&lt;br&gt;Budget diff ≤ 2000 → +15 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Sleep time within 1 hr → +15 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Wake time within 1 hr → +10 pts&lt;br&gt;Cleanliness diff ≤ 1 → +15 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Study habit diff ≤ 1 → +10 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Noise tolerance diff ≤ 1 → +10 pts&lt;br&gt;Same smoking pref → +10 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Same food pref → +5 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Same city → +10 pts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Max score: 100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Labels: Excellent Match (≥85) | Good Match (≥70) | Moderate Match (≥50) | Low Match (&amp;lt;50)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="580" x="1250" y="870" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
